      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782143450873,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Problem framing:\n* This is an outbound call orchestration platform. \nThe core challenge is turning very large campaign uploads into independently schedulable call tasks, \nthen safely moving those tasks through eligibility checks, dispatch, provider callbacks, retries, \nand CRM outcome delivery. The hardest parts are respecting each contact’s local calling window, enforcing per-campaign concurrency caps, \nisolating failures per call attempt, and delivering outcomes to the client CRM within 60 seconds with at-least-once guarantees.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Problem framing:\n* This is an outbound call orchestration platform. \nThe core challenge is turning very large campaign uploads into independently schedulable call tasks, \nthen safely moving those tasks through eligibility checks, dispatch, provider callbacks, retries, \nand CRM outcome delivery. The hardest parts are respecting each contact’s local calling window, enforcing per-campaign concurrency caps, \nisolating failures per call attempt, and delivering outcomes to the client CRM within 60 seconds with at-least-once guarantees.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
